		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Hi.<br><br>I dare say, never give up.&nbsp;&nbsp;Being a paladin is hard, but rewarding. I am now Lvl 37, and the only gear I have ever owned was stuff I killed for/purchaced. I am also on a PvP server, which adds even more trials.  As a note, When solo, I gain XP faster than I do in a group, and that is saying something.  With LOH and your healing spells, you have the equivilent of 3x your HP in your use.  Equipment is very key.  Always get the best you can.  I am not the best equipped, but Im not that bad off.  Go for AC above stats, as AC makes the most difference.  Thats about all I can say.<br><br>Winterknight<br>lvl 37 paladin <br>Vallon Zek</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
